 add to auto-converted links</li><li>Add rel-nofollow to any links parsed in comments</li><li>Add sqlsrv support for Revolution 2.1+ installs</li><li>&#91;#4124&#93; Add fix for threads that have complex names</li><li>&#91;#3519&#93; Add pre and post Hooks to Quip</li><li>&#91;#3523&#93; Add field-specific error messages, ensure validation of those fields happens on first submit</li><li>&#91;#3518&#93; Enable one-click post options bypassing preview, and added requirePreview property to force preview if wanted</li><li>Fix bug with replyUrl in threaded comments and requireAuth</li></ul><ul>\n</ul>\n<p><b></b></p><ul>\n</ul>";s:9:"createdon";s:24:"2012-12-19T16:19:39+0000";s:9:"createdby";s:8:"opengeek";s:8:"editedon";s:24:"2016-10-02T11:07:58+0000";s:10:"releasedon";s:24:"2012-12-19T16:19:39+0000";s:9:"downloads";s:5:"58523";s:8:"approved";s:4:"true";s:7:"audited";s:4:"true";s:8:"featured";s:4:"true";s:10:"deprecated";s:5:"false";s:7:"license";s:5:"GPLv2";s:7:"smf_url";s:0:"";s:10:"repository";s:24:"4d4c3fa6b2b0830da9000001";s:8:"supports";s:3:"2.2";s:8:"location";s:60:"http://modx.com/extras/download/?id=50d1e920f245544b75000020";s:9:"signature";s:13:"quip-2.3.3-pl";s:11:"supports_db";s:12:"mysql,sqlsrv";s:16:"minimum_supports";s:3:"2.2";s:9:"breaks_at";s:8:"10000000";s:10:"screenshot";s:51:"http://modx.s3.amazonaws.com/extras/538/quipss2.png";s:4:"file";a:7:{s:2:"id";s:24:"50d1e920f245544b75000020";s:7:"version";s:24:"50d1e91bf245544b7500001e";s:8:"filename";s:27:"quip-2.3.3-pl.transport.zip";s:9:"downloads";s:5:"18277";s:6:"lastip";s:13:"31.202.205.87";s:9:"transport";s:4:"true";s:8:"location";s:60:"http://modx.com/extras/download/?id=50d1e920f245544b75000020";}s:17:"package-signature";s:13:"quip-2.3.3-pl";s:10:"categories";s:28:"blogging,commenting-feedback";s:4:"tags";s:22:"blog,blogging,comments";}', 2, 3, 3, 'pl', 0);
